## Diagnostic

### Gets the current log level of the logger
POST  {{baseUrl}}/system/v1/diagnostics/reconfigureLogLevel?minLogLevel=Debug&maxLogLevel=Fatal&loggerName=Meshmakers.*

### Sets log level of Microsoft to debug
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/v1/diagnostics/reconfigureLogLevel?minLogLevel=Info&maxLogLevel=Fatal&loggerName=Microsoft.*

### Sets log level of Microsoft to warn
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/v1/diagnostics/reconfigureLogLevel?minLogLevel=Warn&maxLogLevel=Fatal&loggerName=Microsoft.*

### Sets log level of Microsoft to off
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/v1/diagnostics/reconfigureLogLevel?minLogLevel=Off&maxLogLevel=Off&loggerName=Microsoft.*




## MCP Tool Tests

### List Tools
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "tools/list"
}


### Echo Tool - Basic Test
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "Echo",
    "arguments": {
      "message": "Hello OctoMesh!"
    }
  }
}


### Get Available Types
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_available_types",
    "arguments": {
      "includeAbstract": false
    }
  }
}

### Search Types
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
