### Get Type Schema
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{tenantId}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 5,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_type_schema",
    "arguments": {
